# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SolReclaim — Environment Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env to source control.
#
# RPC PROVIDER — Recommended: Helius (https://helius.dev)
# Helius is the best choice for this dApp because it provides:
#   1. getParsedTokenAccountsByOwner — for account scanning
#   2. getAssetBatch (DAS API) — for token names / logos
#   3. sendSmartTransaction — for MEV-protected sends
#   4. Priority fee estimation
#   5. Generous free tier (100k req/day)
#
# Steps:
#   1. Sign up at https://dev.helius.xyz
#   2. Create a new API key under "Mainnet"
#   3. Paste the RPC URL below
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Option A: Provide just the API key (recommended)
VITE_HELIUS_API_KEY=YOUR_API_KEY_HERE

# Option B: Provide full RPC URL (overrides API key)
VITE_HELIUS_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_API_KEY_HERE

# Optional: Devnet for testing
# VITE_HELIUS_RPC_URL=https://devnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_API_KEY_HERE
